<br>
Quad kite dire wolves, then giants as you get enough mana.  I think you are right on the lower end of having enough mana to put away scouts but I can remember.  The higher level the giant, the more faction you get in return.  Stick to wolves and scouts... elites will have too many HP.<br>
<br>
